l foreground subtraction and\ninstrument calibration. Conversely, these could become the first non-trivial\nreionization scenarios to be ruled out by 21 cm experiments, thereby\nconstraining the contribution of AGN to reionization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Jan 2017 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 May 2017 12:48:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-17"}
