deals, i.e. the lattice-ordered group generated by it when one\nproceeds as if its elements are comparable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2017 07:54:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Jan 2018 22:47:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 26 Oct 2018 17:44:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-29"}
